title: Cinema 4D R15.057 (with Keygen)
description:
Installation is simple!

1. Mount or burn C4D_R15.iso under "Maxon Cinema 4D R15 Installation Files"
2. During the installation, it will ask for a serial number, open the keygen under "Keygen" and click "Generate"
3. Paste the serial number into the installation
4. Complete the installation
5. Open Cinema 4D
6. Click Help > Manual Installation
7. Select the update file under "C4D R15.037 (1st)", let it update
8. Repeat the process for the file under "C4D R15.057 (2nd)"
9. You're done!

Please seed, as this is a BIG file. Enjoy!
